STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Eric R. SHAW a/k/a Kenneth Williams, and Tyrone Johnson, Defendant-Petitioner. C-151 September Term 2018
080914 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 5, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001533-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
